# Settings for 'astyle'
# These settings are based on the Google C++ Style Guide.

# I referred to the following pages to find the options:
# http://astyle.sourceforge.net/astyle.html
# https://google.github.io/styleguide/cppguide.html
# https://stackoverflow.com/questions/23684451/astyle-for-google-c-style-guide

# Brace Style Options:
--style=google

# Tab Options:
--indent=spaces=2

# Indentation Options:
--indent-modifiers
--indent-switches

# Padding Options:
--pad-header
--pad-oper
--align-pointer=name

# Formatting Options:
--keep-one-line-blocks
--keep-one-line-statements

# Other Options:
--suffix=none
--preserve-date
--lineend=linux
